      <txt c="X" a="X" r="X" s="2" w="850" x="40" y="80" delay="0" pt="1" e="-3" align="left">All of the ship's paperwork was in order. Customs officials asked the Captain for some cigarettes as they did not want to leave the ship "empty-handed". After long negotiations, the Captain agreed to give the Customs officials one pack of cigarettes only.

How would the cigarettes be considered?</txt>
